OL,3,CWoman charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter pedestrians hit by car in London
OL,6,FA woman has been charged with
OL,7,Fattempted murder after a car hit
OL,8,Fpedestrians in central London in the
OL,9,Fearly hours of Sunday.
OL,11,FPolice named the woman as 29-year-old
OL,12,FGabrielle Carrington of Broadfield
OL,13,FRoad, Manchester.
OL,15,FA woman in her 30s remains in a life-
OL,16,Fthreatening condition, and a man in
OL,17,Fhis 50s suffered life-changing
OL,18,Finjuries after they were hit by a car
OL,19,Fin Argyll Street, Westminster, at
OL,20,Faround 4.30am on Sunday, the
OL,21,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
