OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776723068
OL,3,CWoman charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter pedestrians hit by car in London
OL,6,FA second woman, who is also in her
OL,7,F30s, suffered minor injuries.
OL,9,FCarrington has been charged with
OL,10,Fattempted murder, grievous bodily harm
OL,11,Fwith intent, actual bodily harm and
OL,12,Fdrink driving, police said on Monday
OL,13,Fevening.
OL,15,FThe Crown Prosecution Service said
OL,16,FCarrington was also charged with
OL,17,Fdangerous driving.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
