OL,3,CWoman charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter pedestrians hit by car in London
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FShe has been remanded in custody ahead
OL,12,Fof her first appearance at Westminster
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday.
OL,15,FPolice said the incident, which took
OL,16,Fplace on the Soho street which is home
OL,17,Fto the London Palladium theatre, is
OL,18,Fnot being treated as terrorism-related.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
