OL,3,CWoman charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter pedestrians hit by car in London
OL,6,FDavid Malone, deputy chief crown
OL,7,Fprosecutor in London North, said: "We
OL,8,Fremind all concerned that proceedings
OL,9,Fagainst the defendant are active and
OL,10,Fthat she has the right to a fair trial.
OL,12,F"It is vital that there should be no
OL,13,Freporting, commentary or sharing of
OL,14,Finformation online which could in any
OL,15,Fway prejudice these proceedings."
OL,17,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,18,Fcontact police on 101, providing the
OL,19,Freference 3374/19APR.
